sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Web
    participant Server as gRPC Server
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant GH as GitHub Contents API
    %% Write path: Web → PostgreSQL → GitHub
    User->>Web: Create/Update/Delete case
    Web->>Server: CreateCase / UpdateCase / DeleteCase (gRPC)
    Server->>PG: Write case
    PG-->>Server: OK
    Server->>GH: PUT /repos/{owner}/{repo}/contents/cases/{path}.md
    Note over Server,GH: Uses installation token (GitHub App JWT)
    GH-->>Server: 200 OK (or 409 stale SHA)
    alt 409 Conflict (stale SHA)
        Server->>GH: GET current file SHA
        GH-->>Server: Current SHA
        Server->>GH: PUT with current SHA (PostgreSQL wins)
        GH-->>Server: 200 OK
    end
    Server-->>Web: Response

    %% GitHub App not configured
    Note over Server,GH: If GitHub App not configured → skip push, log warning, return success
